750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*dcdVATcm0yJQxr4jGG5bFA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*dcdVATcm0yJQxr4jGG5bFA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*dcdVATcm0yJQxr4jGG5bFA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*dcdVATcm0yJQxr4jGG5bFA.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/700/1*dcdVATcm0yJQxr4jGG5bFA.png"></picture></div><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Keeping track of state in our model makes it possible to not just predict the most likely <em>first</em> letter in the story, but to predict the most likely <em>next</em> letter given all previous letters.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">This is the basic idea of a <em>Recurrent </em>Neural Network. We are updating the network each time we use it. This allows it to update its predictions based on what it saw most recently. It can even model patterns over time as long as we give it enough of a memory.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">What’s a single letter good for?</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Predicting the next letter in a story might seem pretty useless. What’s the point?</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">One cool use might be auto-predict for a mobile phone keyboard:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
