            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We’ve replaced each object in the level with a letter:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">‘-’ is a blank space</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">‘=’ is a solid block</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">‘#’ is a breakable brick</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">‘?’ is a coin block</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
